snippet.title: 'Stick 'Em Up 2: Paper Adventures' Short Trailer
snippet.description:
HERO TEAM is the spiritual sequel to Stick 'Em Up 2 and is coming out soon. Check it out and wishlist at https://heroteamgame.com/

--

Stick 'Em Up 2 is out now on Windows, Mac, Linux, iOS, and Android

Get the free Starter Edition at http://seu2.com/

Stick 'Em Up 2: Paper Adventures is a run'n'gun/platform game of stick figure characters fighting through beautiful paper and card levels.
